Package: NPSWO
Title: MSE Framework for North Pacific Swordfish
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Adrian", "Hordyk", , "adrian@bluematterscience.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Rebecca", "Scott", , "rscott@bluematterscience.com", role = c("aut")))
Description: A framework for conducting Management Strategy Evaluation (MSE)
    for North Pacific swordfish (Xiphias gladius). Built on the openMSE
    ecosystem, with MSEtool serving as the primary MSE engine. The package
    provides functions specific to the North Pacific swordfish MSE, including
    operating model conditioning, stochastic life-history parameter sampling,
    and Stock Synthesis 3 (SS3) model setup and execution. The root directory
    of the GitHub repository contains all code required to reproduce the
    MSE.
